{"tid":1214944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又發埋啲示威夢","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:05:25.000Z","uid":247937,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd2be6c198a583552022b60de06c5e1bccd76e4b","tid":1214944,"uid":247937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzwPag4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzwPag4.gif&h=4cc2c4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚發夢香港有示威遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺其他Post度見到呢張gif<br />\n證明左人群較為疏散容易對付催淚<br />\n證明左一班人迫埋一齊衝等於俾人一下淚彈收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為恐慌只會令人向後退 明明可以直接淋息粒彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多外國<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和平示威</span>片段睇得出用小隊形式係比較有利 用嚟降低大範圍嘅攻擊例如淚彈同埋橡膠散彈嘅命中率<br />\n就算近距離胡椒噴霧都唔需要因為走唔甩而硬食<br />\n當然個壞處就係容易落單容易被捉 但係你見警隊本身都係用小隊形式就知咩事<br />\n佢哋齊裝係一回事 當日個陣效率低係一回事 好多片段都見到因為前面比後面走得慢頂住晒硬食好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有陣嘅小隊游擊可以係一個方向<br />\nAnyway 冇裝輸七成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱上面個夢好<br />\n好恐怖"},{"pid":"261eb08588fbe79f426f0769fb7e51a98779d4d7","tid":1214944,"uid":247937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd2be6c198a583552022b60de06c5e1bccd76e4b","tid":1214944,"uid":247937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzwPag4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzwPag4.gif&h=4cc2c4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚發夢香港有示威遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺其他Post度見到呢張gif<br />\n證明左人群較為疏散容易對付催淚<br />\n證明左一班人迫埋一齊衝等於俾人一下淚彈收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為恐慌只會令人向後退 明明可以直接淋息粒彈<img src=\"/asse